{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act19side_level_act19side_01_beg","storyGroup":"act19side","storySort":2,"storyDependence":"act19side_level_act19side_st01","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"DV-1","storyName":"特里蒙街道","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"博士与Mechanist前往小巷调查缪尔赛思失踪一事，遇到伏击；城外，拓荒者想以人质为筹码得到自由，却遭到拒绝。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act19side/level_act19side_01_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act19side_01","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":0,"next":2,"characters":["Mechanist","玛丽","莱茵防卫科成员","赫默","格雷伊","桑尼","拓荒队成员","埃琳娜","莱茵实验员","？？？","斐尔迪南","霍尔海雅"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4d/Avg_bg_29_g6_mainstreet.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":8},{"type":"text","text":"3:56 P.M. 天气/阴","id":9},{"type":"text","text":"特里蒙主城区","id":10},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1$1","id":11},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"这是你第三遍浏览白面鸮的个人记录了，博士。","id":12,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"你有没有什么新发现？","id":13,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":14},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","focus":"-1","id":15},{"type":"decision","options":[{"id":"17","text":"白面鸮的记录有着丰富的细节。"},{"id":"24","text":"拓荒队领队受过良好教育。"},{"id":"30","text":"埃琳娜的咖啡应该挺香的。"}],"values":[],"id":16},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":17,"end":22},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":18},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"白面鸮的脑部植入了某种特殊芯片。","id":19,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"“九号装置”——梅尔这么称呼它。这应该是莱茵生命对这项技术的内部代号。","id":20,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"它直接连接着白面鸮的脑部神经，作为大脑的一部分正常运作着，同时也记录着她各个脑区神经活动的数据。","id":21,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"也就是说，你刚才看到的，就是白面鸮的视觉处理器——她的双眼记录的一切。","id":22,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":23},{"type":"predicate","references":["2"],"id":24,"end":28},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":25},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"哥伦比亚拓荒队的成员什么出身都有。","id":26,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"对当前生活不满的年轻人，欠了债日子过不下去的中年夫妇，小偷小摸被抓住了又不想蹲大牢的罪犯——","id":27,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"当然，还有无力支付高额保险费用，又不甘心被关在收治区的感染者。","id":28,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":29},{"type":"predicate","references":["3"],"id":30,"end":33},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":31},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"我还是对弗兰克斯使用的提神试剂更感兴趣。","id":32,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"下班之后的酒精是很美妙，但工作时喝那么多液体，也未免太容易打断思路了。","id":33,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":34,"end":true},{"type":"useless","references":["1","2","3"],"id":35},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":36},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"从白面鸮同步给我们的记录来看，除她之外，同为罗德岛合作干员、就职于莱茵生命能量科的埃琳娜......","id":37,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"连同莱茵生命源石技艺应用科主任多萝西·弗兰克斯，一起遭到了拓荒者的绑架。","id":38,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"而几乎与此同时，塞雷娅告诉我们，莱茵生命生态科主任缪尔赛思在发出紧急求援信息之后就失踪了，目前生死未卜。","id":39,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":40},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","focus":"-1","id":41},{"type":"decision","options":[{"id":"43","text":"莱茵生命是不是出事了？"},{"id":"47","text":"......"},{"id":"51","text":"难道做研究也是高危工作？"}],"values":[],"id":42},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":43,"end":45},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"目前来看，是。","id":45,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":46},{"type":"predicate","references":["2"],"id":47,"end":49},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":48},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"......","id":49,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":50},{"type":"predicate","references":["3"],"id":51,"end":53},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":52},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"欢迎来到哥伦比亚。","id":53,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":54,"end":true},{"type":"useless","references":["1","2","3"],"id":55},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"能让塞雷娅向罗德岛求助，莱茵生命目前很大几率已经陷入危机。","id":57,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"幸亏本舰就在附近，否则我们也很难迅速作出反应。","id":58,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"虽然绑架事件发生在距离特里蒙城一百多公里的新基地，但凯尔希担心此事与先前被叫停的那些实验有关。","id":59,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":60},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","focus":"-1","id":61},{"type":"decision","options":[{"id":"63","text":"那个基地是做什么的？"},{"id":"67","text":"源石变异实验......"},{"id":"71","text":"再介绍下特里蒙吧。"}],"values":[],"id":62},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":63,"end":65},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":64},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"对外资料显示，那是一个正在建设中的普通实验场所。","id":65,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":66},{"type":"predicate","references":["2"],"id":67,"end":69},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":68},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"在进入特里蒙之前，凯尔希向我们开放了所有相关档案的权限。","id":69,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":70},{"type":"predicate","references":["3"],"id":71,"end":73},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":72},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"这座城市是哥伦比亚的科学与技术中心。数百家科技公司将总部设在特里蒙。","id":73,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":74,"end":true},{"type":"useless","references":["1","2","3"],"id":75},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":76},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"“炎魔事件”“洛肯水箱”“伐木场”。","id":77,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"上述每一个名词都对应了一位我们罗德岛的干员，背后更是牵涉了数百个类似的实验。","id":78,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"这些实验大多涉及源石对生物细胞的变异作用，每一项都非常危险。","id":79,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"在哥伦比亚，大型科技公司比如莱茵生命往往并不直接参与类似具有高风险的实验。","id":80,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"他们会将实验委托给规模较小的机构，雇佣拓荒队，在城市边缘的荒地上建立相应的基地来完成实验工作。","id":81,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"此次事件中，白面鸮所在的359号基地就是其中一处。","id":82,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":83},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","focus":"-1","id":84},{"type":"decision","options":[{"id":"86","text":"我记得你过去的工作经历......"},{"id":"86","text":"你是不是也在类似基地工作过？"}],"values":[],"id":85},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":86,"end":96},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":87},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"工作？我并不想把那段经历称作“工作”。","id":88,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"那些大企业“剽窃”了我的创作，把它们应用到了不该应用的地方。","id":89,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"看到五十米外的广告牌了吗？“沃尔沃特科钦斯基家用自动爆米花机，更快更甜更稳定。”","id":90,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"它的能源核心原型草图还留在我的终端上。","id":91,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"最初它该用在荒地路面自动清理机内部，可是我的主管断定这款产品一定卖不出去。","id":92,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"他说，哪家人力资源公司会愿意为拓荒者购买更好的装备？","id":93,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"后来我带着思路来到了罗德岛，我们的航线排障工程队正在使用的就是最新型号。","id":94,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"我早就知道，无论是沃尔沃特科钦斯基，还是莱茵生命，这些所谓的科技公司，它们最终会被自己的造物摧毁——","id":95,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"因为它们从未尊重过创造本身。","id":96,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":97},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","focus":"-1","id":98},{"type":"decision","options":[{"id":"100","text":"缪尔赛思难道正被自己的实验品追杀？"},{"id":"100","text":"白面鸮不会被恐怖实验体绑架了吧？！"}],"values":[],"id":99},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":100,"end":105},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":101},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"......","id":102,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"我该笑一下吗，博士？","id":103,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"毕竟，你说的可能不是什么科幻故事，或者一个荒诞笑话。","id":104,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"它很可能是明天的新闻。","id":105,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":106},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","focus":"-1","id":107},{"type":"decision","options":[{"id":"109","text":"难怪可露希尔对你又佩服又害怕......"},{"id":"114","text":"......"},{"id":"118","text":"你和Logos不愧是好搭档。"}],"values":[],"id":108},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":109,"end":112},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":110},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"你是指，她偶尔会兼任我的新武器测试用靶？","id":111,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"只要别拿靠不住的点子打扰我工作，她就没必要感到害怕。","id":112,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":113},{"type":"predicate","references":["2"],"id":114,"end":116},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":115},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"......","id":116,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":117},{"type":"predicate","references":["3"],"id":118,"end":122},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":119},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"作为搭档，Logos是还不错。","id":120,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"不过博士，你能提醒一下他吗？","id":121,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"要是他能省略一些修辞，任务耗时将缩短至少三十个百分点，我能把更多时间花在真正的工作上。","id":122,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":123,"end":true},{"type":"useless","references":["1","2","3"],"id":124},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":125},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"情报梳理完毕，博士。","id":126,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"目前有用的信息就只有这么多了。我已将最重要的几份文档提高了查阅优先级，你随时能通过PRTS读取。","id":127,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":128},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","focus":"-1","id":129},{"type":"decision","options":[{"id":"131","text":"还有没有新消息？"}],"values":[],"id":130},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":131,"end":135},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":132},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"白面鸮的记录在这之后就没更新过。","id":133,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"经过梅尔的调整，九号装置的数据传输趋于稳定。","id":134,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"除非白面鸮的身体出现了问题......","id":135,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":136},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","focus":"-1","id":137},{"type":"decision","options":[{"id":"139","text":"我有些担心白面鸮。"},{"id":"139","text":"希望赫默与格雷伊能尽快见到白面鸮。"}],"values":[],"id":138},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":139,"end":143},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":140},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"赫默会随时通知我们基地那边的进展。","id":141,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"塞雷娅已经收到消息，她一个小时后就会与我们会合。","id":142,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"博士，在这段时间内，你还有什么计划吗？","id":143,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":144},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","focus":"-1","id":145},{"type":"decision","options":[{"id":"147","text":"去缪尔赛思出事的地方看看。"}],"values":[],"id":146},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":147,"end":149},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":148},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"我是个机械师，不是什么侦探助手......","id":149,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":150},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","focus":"-1","id":151},{"type":"decision","options":[{"id":"153","text":"但这是目前我们唯一能做的事。"},{"id":"153","text":"我也只是个源石研究者。"}],"values":[],"id":152},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":153},{"type":"decision","options":[{"id":"155","text":"我只能依靠你了，Mechanist。"}],"values":[],"id":154},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":155,"end":158},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":156},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"好吧，博士，那现在就出发。","id":157,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"但愿明天就能回到本舰，见到我亲爱的工作台。","id":158,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":159},{"type":"dialog","id":160},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":161},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":162},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":163},{"type":"character","id":164},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/ac/Avg_bg_29_g2_edgeofbase.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":165},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":166},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$mist_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_mist_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":167,"musicid":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":168},{"type":"delay","time":"2","text":"","id":169},{"type":"text","text":"6:47 P.M. 天气/阴","id":170},{"type":"text","text":"特里蒙城外，359号实验基地监控站","id":171},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":172},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"基地里面的人有没有发来新的消息？","id":173,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":174},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱茵防卫科成员","text":"没有，警长。","id":175,"figure":["avg_npc_528_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":176},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"你联系过你们莱茵的那个什么斐尔迪南主任了吧？他到底什么时候能来？","id":177,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":178},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱茵防卫科成员","text":"斐尔迪南主任正在......开会。","id":179,"figure":["avg_npc_528_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":180},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"开会？你跟我说他还在开会？什么会议比他手下员工的性命更重要？","id":181,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"该死！","id":182,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"把望远镜给我。","id":183,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":184},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱茵防卫科成员","text":"啊......好的。","id":185,"figure":["avg_npc_528_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"你是不是不相信那群拓荒者真的会动手？","id":187,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"我告诉你，他们会。","id":188,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"真被逼急了，他们什么都做得出来。","id":189,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":190},{"type":"character","id":191},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":192},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1027_greyy2_1#1$2","name2":"avg_108_silent_1#1$1","fadetime":"1.5","id":193},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":194},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1027_greyy2_1#1$2","name2":"avg_108_silent_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":195},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"您的意思是，我们在基地里的同事会有生命危险？","id":196,"figure":["avg_108_silent_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":197},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"......你是谁？","id":198,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1027_greyy2_1#1$2","name2":"avg_108_silent_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":199},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"奥利维亚·赫默，莱茵生命研究员，也是罗德岛制药的合作医疗干员。","id":200,"figure":["avg_108_silent_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"这位是我在罗德岛的同事，就职于工程部的格雷伊先生。","id":201,"figure":["avg_108_silent_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1027_greyy2_1#4$2","name2":"avg_108_silent_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":202},{"type":"jump","name":"left","power":"5","times":"2","fadetime":"0.51","block":"true","id":203},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格雷伊","text":"您、您好！我是罗德岛的电气工程师......不过我还在实习期！","id":204,"figure":["avg_1027_greyy2_1",13]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":205},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"罗德岛？那又是什么公司？","id":206,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1027_greyy2_1#5$2","name2":"avg_108_silent_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":207},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格雷伊","text":"呃......","id":208,"figure":["avg_1027_greyy2_1",14]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":209},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"算了，也不用跟我解释。在特里蒙，短短一天就能有几十家不同名号的新公司冒出来。","id":210,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"你也算是莱茵生命的对吧？你在你们公司能说得上话吗？","id":211,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1027_greyy2_1#5$2","name2":"avg_108_silent_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":212},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"说得上话？女士，我不是很明白您的意思......","id":213,"figure":["avg_108_silent_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":214},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"行了，我知道你不是什么负责人。","id":215,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"你一看就是那种......在书堆里泡着的学者，就和里面那几位人质一样。","id":216,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"你们根本不懂怎么跟那群人打交道。","id":217,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1027_greyy2_1#5$2","name2":"avg_108_silent_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":218},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我听说他们是在基地工作的拓荒队成员......","id":219,"figure":["avg_108_silent_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":220},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"......拓荒者。","id":221,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"这么好听的名字，只适合放在广告招牌上。","id":222,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"而我最清楚他们都是什么人。罪犯、赌徒、没钱治病的感染者......走上荒野的时候，他们已经一无所有。","id":223,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1027_greyy2_1#1$2","name2":"avg_108_silent_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":224},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格雷伊","text":"请问......我们可以同他们聊聊吗？","id":225,"figure":["avg_1027_greyy2_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1027_greyy2_1#6$2","name2":"avg_108_silent_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":226},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格雷伊","text":"您或许注意到了，我和赫默医生都是感染者。我们能理解他们的处境。","id":227,"figure":["avg_1027_greyy2_1",15]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":228},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"莱茵生命，还有那个什么罗德岛都挣了很多钱，是吧？","id":229,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"你们背后有一家还算有“良心”的企业为你们支付保险账单——这才是关键。","id":230,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"所以，别说什么你们能互相理解的傻话了。","id":231,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1027_greyy2_1#5$2","name2":"avg_108_silent_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":232},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格雷伊","text":"保险账单？是哪个方面的......","id":233,"figure":["avg_1027_greyy2_1",14]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1027_greyy2_1#5$2","name2":"avg_108_silent_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":234},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"......是哥伦比亚针对感染者的特殊政策。","id":235,"figure":["avg_108_silent_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"女士，请相信我们——罗德岛是一家致力于解决感染者问题的医药公司。","id":236,"figure":["avg_108_silent_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":237},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"解决问题？如果我给你一把弩，你能从这里帮我把绑匪们摆平吗？","id":238,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1027_greyy2_1#5$2","name2":"avg_108_silent_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":239},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"......我不能。","id":240,"figure":["avg_108_silent_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我是一名医生。","id":241,"figure":["avg_108_silent_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":242},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"他可以吗？","id":243,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1027_greyy2_1#4$2","name2":"avg_108_silent_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":244},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格雷伊","text":"我？不，不行的，我想我们还没到必须战斗的那一步......","id":245,"figure":["avg_1027_greyy2_1",13]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":246},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"那看来你们帮不上什么忙了。","id":247,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":248},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":249},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":250},{"type":"character","id":251},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/64/Avg_bg_29_g3_cottage.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":252},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":253},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0"