]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"罗德岛不会只派两名干员去基地。别忘了，他们和塞雷娅一直有联系。","id":449,"figure":["avg_npc_522_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","name2":"char_empty","focus":"-1","id":450},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"哦？又是你们的防卫科主任？","id":451,"figure":["avg_npc_522_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","name2":"char_empty","focus":"1","id":452},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"因为塞雷娅，我们的实验已经耽搁得够久了......我和上校都快失去耐心了。","id":453,"figure":["avg_npc_522_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"记住，这一次不要让他们找到任何东西。","id":454,"figure":["avg_npc_522_1",5]},{"type":"dialog","id":455},{"type":"playsound","key":"$transmission","volume":"0.9","id":456},{"type":"charactercutin","widgetID":"1","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":457},{"type":"delay","time":"0.8","id":458},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":459},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":460},{"type":"character","id":461},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1$1","id":462},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/49/Avg_bg_29_g8_alley_n.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":463},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":464},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":465},{"type":"delay","time":"2","text":"","id":466},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1$1","id":467},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"我们到了，博士。","id":468,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"塞雷娅收到的最后一条信息就是从这条巷子里发出去的。","id":469,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":470},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","focus":"-1","id":471},{"type":"decision","options":[{"id":"473","text":"看起来很普通。"},{"id":"477","text":"距离莱茵生命总部不是很近。"},{"id":"481","text":"就在商业区旁边。"}],"values":[],"id":472},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":473,"end":475},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":474},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"在特里蒙，类似的巷子有好几百条。","id":475,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":476},{"type":"predicate","references":["2"],"id":477,"end":479},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":478},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"从这里到莱茵生命总部有至少三十分钟车程。","id":479,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":480},{"type":"predicate","references":["3"],"id":481,"end":484},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":482},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"当时塞雷娅就在商业区。","id":483,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"她正在等缪尔赛思，她们约了见面。","id":484,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":485,"end":true},{"type":"useless","references":["1","2","3"],"id":486},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","focus":"-1","id":487},{"type":"decision","options":[{"id":"489","text":"看来缪尔赛思是被追到这里的。"}],"values":[],"id":488},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":489,"end":492},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":490},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"要是没有人追赶的话，她一定不会选择走进这条小巷。","id":491,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"无论对方是谁，在大街上动手的风险显然要高得多。","id":492,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":493},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","focus":"-1","id":494},{"type":"decision","options":[{"id":"496","text":"赫默提到过缪尔赛思的能力。"},{"id":"496","text":"塞雷娅提交过关于缪尔赛思的报告。"}],"values":[],"id":495},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":496,"end":502},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":497},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"嗯......搜索完毕。","id":498,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"“操纵水分子的能力”——能量转换型还是物质重构型源石技艺？不管是什么原理，看着都挺强的。","id":499,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"“水分身”——肉眼完全无法看出破绽？","id":500,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"这就更有意思了。从事实验研究的人，就和我们机械师一样，观察能力通常都很敏锐。","id":501,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"连赫默和梅尔都上当了的话，这可不是一般的法术幻象。","id":502,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":503},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","focus":"-1","id":504},{"type":"decision","options":[{"id":"506","text":"缪尔赛思战斗力不弱。"},{"id":"506","text":"缪尔赛思自保能力很强。"},{"id":"506","text":"缪尔赛思简直既能打又能跑啊。"}],"values":[],"id":505},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":506,"end":510},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":507},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"地面上留下了一些灼烧的痕迹。","id":508,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"范围不是很广......动手的人极有可能是利用某种技术设备定向加热了缪尔赛思周围的空气。","id":509,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"考虑到她的源石技艺极度依赖水分子，这说明，她的对手很了解她。","id":510,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":511},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","focus":"-1","id":512},{"type":"decision","options":[{"id":"514","text":"就像我们了解她一样。"}],"values":[],"id":513},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":514,"end":517},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":515},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"你是说......","id":516,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"对方有可能也是莱茵内部的人？","id":517,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":518},{"type":"playsound","key":"$e_atk_cadkgt_s_lp","volume":"0.9","id":519},{"type":"stopmusic","id":520},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":521},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"博士，小心！","id":522,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":523},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"-200","fadetime":"0.51","id":524},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id"